{"tid":2382569,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Lotus 宣布 Elise/Exige/Evora 2021年正式停產","createTime":"2021-01-27T10:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T06:41:46.000Z","uid":134233,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4bedda1d8478260982945a8088a542dfbeac6c9e","tid":2382569,"uid":134233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"1995年，Lotus Elise以其輕量化的車架為跑車界帶來革命性的轉變，至今亦深受車迷歡迎。2000年，由Elise衍生而出的Lotus Exige正式面世，因為能同時兼顧道路及賽道上的不同需要，旋即被譽為「道路上的賽車」。2008年，Lotus Evora以結合操控性，實用性及舒適性的獨特風格，成功打入高級跑車市場，成為一時佳話。<br />\n<br />\n2021年，為配合廠方Vision80的發展計劃，所有現行型號將於2021年正式停產，以迎接全新世代跑車，帶領Lotus走向另一巔峰。<br />\n<br />\n全線Lotus型號最後一年之生產配額現正接受預訂，請即把握最後機會，與我們聯絡以了解更多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CKi2-wuhrO5/?igshid=1hb16kxiroulu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCKi2-wuhrO5%2F%3Figshid%3D1hb16kxiroulu&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn5FDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=d896b668\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCKi2-wuhrO5%2F%3Figshid%3D1hb16kxiroulu&h=6f40b20a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CKi2-wuhrO5/?igshid=1hb16kxiroulu</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b86f670c2d54fd64d41dcadf8e9af7ceb5cf34","tid":2382569,"uid":78517,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T11:40:18.000Z","msg":"冇人買，遲早執笠"},{"pid":"249c863b834ca908ab050925ce3d6526572cef08","tid":2382569,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T11:53:59.000Z","msg":"果然咁hardcore嘅車係冇人青睞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5e5bfb8836d76e662e262db1c1d79c7bcc6a8a","tid":2382569,"uid":151927,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"249c863b834ca908ab050925ce3d6526572cef08","tid":2382569,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"repl